## 📱 The Mobile-First Revolution

Over 50% of web traffic is mobile. We don't build "desktop sites" anymore; we build sites that **adapt**.

---

## 1️⃣ Media Queries

Media queries allow you to apply CSS only if a condition is met (like screen width).

```css
/* Standard Layout (Mobile) */
.card { width: 100%; }

/* Desktop Layout (Screen >= 768px) */
@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .card { width: 50%; }
}
```

---

## 2️⃣ Viewport Meta Tag

Without this tag, mobile browsers will assume you're on a desktop and scale down the text until it's unreadable.

```html
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
```

---

## 3️⃣ Fluid Typography & Images

*   `font-size: 1.5rem;` - Scales based on user browser settings.
*   `max-width: 100%; height: auto;` - Ensures images never overflow their container.
